name: Duality of Thought
description:
Inspired by the Japanese art of
Kintsugi- the process of restoring
broken pottery using gold and other
precious metals. The cracks are an
area to celebrate, rather than
focusing on the missing pieces, often
symbolizing rebirth. What one may
view as broken is beautiful to another.
(Cinema 4D/Octane Render/PS)
2400x3000 portrait aspect 300dpi
